== Occupations in geology ==
The [[Dictionary of Occupational Titles]] lists the following occupations in Geology, which it describes as "concerned with the investigation of the composition, structure, and physical and biological history of the earth's [[Crust (geology)|crust]] and the application of this knowledge in such fields as [[archeology]], [[mining]], [[construction]], and [[environmental impact]]":<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://occupationalinfo.org/defset1_4244.html |title=024 OCCUPATIONS IN GEOLOGY |work=Dictionary Of Occupational Titles |accessdate=2011-04-02}}</ref>

* {{annotated link|Crystallography|Crystallographer}}
* {{annotated link|Geodesist}}
* {{annotated link|Geologist}}
* {{annotated link|Petroleum geologist|Geologist, Petroleum}}
* {{annotated link|Geophysical survey|Geophysical Prospector}}
* {{annotated link|Geophysicist}}
* {{annotated link|Hydrologist}}
* {{annotated link|Mineralogist}}
* {{annotated link|Paleontologist}}
* {{annotated link|Petrologist}}
* {{annotated link|Seismologist}}
* {{annotated link|Stratigrapher}}
* Engineer, Soils<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://occupationalinfo.org/02/024161010.html |title=024.161-010 ENGINEER, SOILS (profess. & kin.)  |work=Dictionary Of Occupational Titles |accessdate=2011-04-02}}</ref>
* Geophysical-Laboratory Chief (Alternate Titles: Director, Geophysical)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://occupationalinfo.org/02/024167010.html |title=024.167-010 GEOPHYSICAL-LABORATORY CHIEF (profess. & kin.) alternate titles: director, geophysical laboratory; engineer, geophysical laboratory; research engineer, geophysical laboratory; superintendent, geophysical laboratory  |work=Dictionary Of Occupational Titles |accessdate=2011-04-02}}</ref>
* Geological Aide (Petrol. & Gas)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://occupationalinfo.org/02/024267010.html |title=024.267-010 GEOLOGICAL AIDE (petrol. & gas) |work=Dictionary Of Occupational Titles |accessdate=2011-04-02}}</ref>
* {{annotated link|Prospecting|Prospector}}
* {{annotated link|Paleontology|Paleontological Helper}}
* Laboratory Assistant (Petrol. & Gas) (Alternate Titles: Analyst, Geochemical Prospecting; Core Analyst; Laboratory Tester)<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://occupationalinfo.org/02/024381010.html |title=024.381-010 LABORATORY ASSISTANT (petrol. & gas) alternate titles: analyst, geochemical prospecting; core analyst; laboratory tester |work=Dictionary Of Occupational Titles |accessdate=2011-04-02}}</ref>

